Class Hour

java.lang.Object
J2_Lab2_Karpenko.taskfirst.Hour
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Hour>
Direct Known Subclasses:
HourWithDates
public class Hour
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Hour>
The Hour class represents an hour with a number of passengers and a comment. It implements the Comparable interface to allow for sorting by the number of passengers.
